Name: HACK_IT
About the game: HACK_IT presents players with all sorts of hacking tasks, from sniffing passwords to taking down servers to even drawing money from accounts. Breach your way into user accounts and explore the unknown. Key Features: Narrative Hacking Experience Interactive Terminal Unique Hacking Tools Characters Attack Servers Keylog Passwords Interactive Desktop Missions Progressive Hacking: Missions will progress and get more complex as you learn new methods of execution. Desktop Missions: Get the full immersive experience with desktop view on some missions, open apps and use them with ease. Hacking Executable: HACK_IT is loaded with loads of hacking applications from money loggers to password fetchers, the hacking network has the tool for your needs. Built For Steam: The game has been designed with Steam Integration, packed with achievements and some trading cards.
